{"tid":2443414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初選案何桂藍不再進行保釋覆核　黃子悅吳敏兒被拒保釋","createTime":"2021-03-12T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T06:21:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"737909f26893a938c6a8a5b3d3a935ab83067606","tid":2443414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580236-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580236-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=860c7bc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580236-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=176ac8ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580236-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n21名涉及初選案，被控「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」的被告，今日在西九龍裁判法院提訊，進行每8日一次，向總裁判官蘇惠德申請保釋的聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n第3節聆訊中午12時後開始，涉及6名被告，其中何桂藍不再進行保釋覆核，但保留每8日到庭一次申請保釋的權利，她一度在律師代表交代完放棄保釋後離開犯人欄，及後被總裁判官蘇惠德叫回，以聽取解釋被告人的權利。<br />\n<br />\n而在第2節的聆訊， 6名被告馮達浚、黃之鋒、胡志偉、朱凱廸、尹兆堅、鄒家成放棄向總裁判官申請保釋的權利，黃子悅及吳敏兒再申請保釋被拒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，多間傳媒機構在開庭前向法庭申請豁免刑事訴訟程序條例下，有關報道保釋聆訊內容的限制，但蘇惠德以被告利益及確保日後審訊公正為由，拒絕有關申請。"},{"pid":"7b60a96d9a291b9307c6ef879fc3380778ed1a7d","tid":2443414,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac99e64a93b6090bdaf934c50573bd1ec55233d","tid":2443414,"uid":121855,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐真係好值得respect 希望大家都借以為鑒<br />\n係日常生活裏面盡你自己嘅最大力去反抗任何不合理嘅強權"},{"pid":"8b67a1ae2c4ab92f8f349c66d1012aed9dcc9864","tid":2443414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}